Alembic migrations for Workout MCP Server.

## Running Migrations

Ensure PostgreSQL is running (see docker-compose.yml):

```bash
docker compose up -d
```

Apply migrations to the development database:

```bash
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/workout_mcp uv run alembic upgrade head
```

Create a new migration after model changes:

```bash
uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of change"
```

Apply migrations to the test database:

```bash
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/workout_mcp_test uv run alembic upgrade head
```
